{"tid":865130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[2017/02] 信號系統更新測試期間一旦出現列車服務受阻或延誤，公司會採取適切措施","createTime":"2018-10-16T18:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T18:21:20.000Z","uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"27ef35101798d7f13059c2052fb65002e0a74efc","tid":865130,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:08:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/02/09/HK1702090008.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2017%2F02%2F09%2FHK1702090008.htm&d=uwHdw7kaQlAOKXL42GgPcdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6d7e5aa3\" target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/02/09/HK1702090008.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵已就不同階段的更換工程，以及測試期間可能出現的風險進行全面評估。一旦出現列車服務受阻或延誤，公司會採取適切措施，包括加派職員協助顧客、透過不同渠道發放車務資訊，以及盡快恢復列車服務。<br />\n<br />\n有無人知佢個全面評估有無諗到今日會壞幾條綫？佢個濕鳩適切措施又幫到啲乜撚嘢？？？"},{"pid":"02299915d2485c8c041fda209dcd7e15bc39dfbd","tid":865130,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:11:46.000Z","msg":"最仆街係朝早6點已經出事都照放人入車站"},{"pid":"25aef31038a8303a0a311648800f7c9c4d14cdf3","tid":865130,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02299915d2485c8c041fda209dcd7e15bc39dfbd","tid":865130,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:11:46.000Z","msg":"最仆街係朝早6點已經出事都照放人入車站"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:20:14.000Z","msg":"不嬲都咁"},{"pid":"08fbf2be5f5b54277bf0138f1e13dbe92811f49c","tid":865130,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25aef31038a8303a0a311648800f7c9c4d14cdf3","tid":865130,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02299915d2485c8c041fda209dcd7e15bc39dfbd","tid":865130,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:11:46.000Z","msg":"最仆街係朝早6點已經出事都照放人入車站"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:20:14.000Z","msg":"不嬲都咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:21:20.000Z","msg":"不嬲都仆街"}]}